841
00:48:47.594 --> 00:48:51.354
regulated pathways. It recruits p300 and Cbp

842
00:48:51.474 --> 00:48:55.384
activity to BCL6 loci and proximal chromatin, and it

843
00:48:55.414 --> 00:48:58.474
demonstrates in vivo efficacy and is non-toxic.

